<P><H1 align=center>DC305 – APPLICATION CREDIT/DEBIT CARD DETAILS</H1>
<P></P>
<P><FONT color=red>Areas shown in red text are mandatory 
and must be completed to proceed.</FONT>            </P>
<P>This screen collects the details of the credit/debit card that will be used 
to collect payment of all fees charged during the application by the lender.</P>
<P><H3>Are you paying the fees by credit/debit card: </H3>Payment may be made by other means, clicking ’Yes’ if credit/debit card is 
being used will enable the other fields on this screen that require completion. 
Clicking ‘No’ will leave all fields inactive.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Card holder’s name: </H3>To be supplied by the 
applicant, it may not necessarily be the applicant paying the fees so may be the 
name of a third party.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Card type: </H3>Select the card type from the drop down 
list.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Card number: </H3>To be supplied by the applicant, 
taken from the credit/debit card.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Issue number: </H3>If the card type is ‘Switch’ this 
field will be mandatory.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Expiry date: </H3>Enter the month and year of the 
expiry date from the card, in the format MM/YY.
<P></P>
